descriptionHTML:
Surprise yourself and your friends! During cinema visit look at your watch in 3D glasses.

FEATURES:

- 2in1: Dark and White Watch Faces
- 12/24 auto-format
- High Resolution Design
- Round and Square watches Support

INSTRUCTION:

1. Install Watch Face
2. Wait a minute
2. Go to Android Wear Application
3. Choose Anaglyph 3D Watch Face
4. Enjoy!

The stereo 3D text effext watch face hase been tested on Moto 360, LG G Watch R, ASUS ZenWatch, Sony SmartWatch and other.
